git clone git@github.com:patric-r/jvmtop.git
cd jvmtop/
mvn install

The jvmtop release is in
jvmtop/target/jvmtop-0.9.0-SNAPSHOT/jvmtop-0.9.0-SNAPSHOT.tar.gz

You can run it with the following options:

./jvmtop --profile --threadnamewidth 400 --width 400 <pid>

(Smaller values for threadnamewidth and width would probably work, but the
defaults are too small.)
